Class Lane

java.lang.Object
com.example.froggeroop.terrain.Lane
Direct Known Subclasses:
Sidewalk, TimeAwareLane
public class Lane extends Object
Generic Lane object that are characterized by being a collection of cells Lanes can be chained (having reference to neighboring lanes)
